						<div class="postbody">The columns are <em>not</em> blended by the SNES hardware itself, but rather by the display device. Using one with sufficient resolution (like an LCD) will indeed show each one individually.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><strong>- BMF</strong>
